'''Cro-Sal-Trei''' was a tribe of [[Eickarie]]s that around 378 BBY, was defeated by the rival tribe [[Hu-shi-crive]]. The [[Chief Commander]] and his family were locked in a watchtower by their enemies and left to die. Later that year, Hu-shi-crive lost the watchtower, and would always keep the secret of the watchtower.

